<div class="text-center py-20">
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
    Turn travel notes into<br>
    <span class="text-indigo-600">magazine-ready articles</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
    Paste your rough notes or upload a .docx file. Our AI transforms them into structured,
    fact-checked articles with source attribution — ready to edit and publish.
  </p>
  <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
    <%= link_to "Get started", new_user_registration_path, class: "bg-indigo-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md text-lg font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700" %>
    <%= link_to "Sign in", new_user_session_path, class: "bg-white text-indigo-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-md text-lg font-medium border border-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50" %>
  </div>
  <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500">
    Free to start &middot; 5 articles/month &middot; <%= link_to "See pricing", pricing_path, class: "text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800" %>
  </p>

  <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left">
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Structured Output</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Articles come with sections, key facts, "best for / not for" callouts, and ethics notes — not just prose.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Source Attribution</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Every claim links back to your original notes so you can fact-check before publishing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Edit Before Publishing</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Review every field, tweak the wording, and only publish when you're happy.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
